title: Appointments to Human Organ Transplant Board
content_text: p> The Government today (February 12) announced the re-appointments of Miss Ophelia Chan Chiu-ling and Miss Wong Hang-yee as Chairman and Vice-Chairman of the Human Organ Transplant Board respectively for a term of three years. At the same time, four serving substantive members and 11 serving panel members of the Board have been re-appointed. All appointments will take effect from February 15, 2016. Details are as follows: Re-appointment of substantive members (for three years):
